	(text "Audio chain — badge_hw_design.md §Audio chain.\nI2S BCK/LRCK/DIN → TM8211 DAC → 10µF coupling → TDA1308 amp → 220µF coupling → PJ-320A.\nGain ≈ 2.1× (100k feedback / 47k input). Virtual ground 10k/10k + 10µF.\n220µF/32Ω → −3 dB at 23 Hz; into 16Ω earbuds → 45 Hz. Don't cheap to 100µF — this is a disco.\nDAC needs LSBJ-format I2S (WS shifted by one BCK vs standard I2S) — firmware PIO note."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 25 25 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
			(justify left top)
		)
